text: Alexandra Grebenyuk (; born 30 October 1990) is a Kazakhstani footballer who plays as a goalkeeper and has appeared for the Kazakhstan women's national team. ==Career== Grebenyuk has been capped for the Kazakhstan national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Kazakhstani women's footballers Category:Kazakhstan women's international footballers Category:Women's association football goalkeepers Category:BIIK Kazygurt players
